18 For the purposes of this section, “eligible
19 charter school” means a public charter school
20 authorized pursuant to the Oklahoma Charter
21 Schools Act and is located within the geographic
22 boundaries of the school district,
23 c. (1) If a board of education proposes to sell, lease,
24 or otherwise transfer a district facility to any
